commit.title: [api] Remove `evar_map` ref combinators.
commit.message:
[api] Remove `evar_map` ref combinators.

All the `evar_map` APIs were deprecated in 8.9, thus we remove the
combinators to discourage this style of programming.

Still a few places do use imperative style, but they are pretty
localized and should be cleaned up separately.
